      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOLLIE'S MAID (1) comes off an average effort last start when seventh at Gosford over 388m behind Electric Assent (23.59) in a Grade 4/5. The form out of her last race has been franked. Can atone. REBORN SCARLETT (8) goes very well this trip starting 14 times for five wins and three minors. Below best last time at Wentworth Park (30.97) in a Grade 5, finishing a 14 length eighth. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. ELLA KNOWS (4) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (23.24) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including four wins. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Can measure up this time. CRANKY CRUISER (2) is worth including.",
